text: Tachikawa Station is a train station that is in Tachikawa, Tokyo, Japan. JR East operates this station. ==Adjacent stations== == Transfer == * Tachikawa- Minami Station (Tama Toshi Monorail Line) * Tachikawa-Kita Station (Tama Toshi Monorail Line) ==References== == Other websites == * JR East Tachikawa Station Category:Railway stations in Tokyo
